OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSome rain or
OL,6,Fdrizzle across the north and west at
OL,7,Ftimes overnight. Drier in the east
OL,8,Fwith a few cloud breaks around the
OL,9,FMoray Firth. West coast mist.
OL,10,
OL,11,CWednesday:FCloudy start with some
OL,12,Fdrizzle in the west. Otherwise
OL,13,Fbecoming largely dry with some
OL,14,Fsunshine breaking through in the east
OL,15,Fwhere it will become very warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
