OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FDry,
OL,6,Fsome warm sunshine in east Thursday,
OL,7,Fcloudier with some rain in west. Dry
OL,8,Fstart in east Friday otherwise cloud
OL,9,Fand rain spreading east. Dry, quite
OL,10,Fcloudy Saturday, brighter west.
